s%20of%20thin%20flank%20steak%20seasoned%20in%20a%20cast-iron%20skillet%20on%20the%20stove.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F664df0f614fb5b23cc5f005d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222735%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ELara%20Walsh%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20steak%20was%20perfectly%20seasoned%2C%20I%20added%20some%20oil%20to%20the%20skillet%20and%20started%20cooking%20the%20beef.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20then%20combined%20portobello%20mushrooms%20and%20onions%20in%20the%20other%20skillet.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Portobello%20mushrooms%20and%20thick-cut%20onion%20slices%20cooking%20in%20a%20skillet%20on%20the%20stove.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F664b970020abc1efe8fbad4f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ELara%20Walsh%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20the%20steak%20was%20cooking%20on%20the%20stove%2C%20I%20added%20the%20whole%20Portobello%20mushrooms%20and%20thick-cut%20onion%20slices%20to%20the%20other%20skillet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ENext%2C%20I%20created%20the%20glaze.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Lara%20brushes%20the%20glaze%20on%20the%20steak%20while%20it's%20cooking%20on%20the%20stove.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F664b9f569fc063e829b2f992%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ELara%20Walsh%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20started%20working%20on%20the%20glazing%20sauce%2C%20which%20is%20made%20from%20a%20combination%20of%20Tabasco%20and%20Worcestershire%20sauce.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUsing%20a%20brush%2C%20I%20began%20painting%20the%20steaks%20and%20the%20veggies%20with%20the%20mixture%20to%20create%20a%20glaze.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAfter%20glazing%20the%20steak%20and%20veggies%2C%20I%20