0and%20I%20think%20I%20may%20have%20added%20too%20much%20because%20the%20liquid%20didn't%20burn%20off%20quickly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20letting%20them%20simmer%20in%20the%20beer%20for%20about%20five%20minutes%2C%20I%20took%20the%20steak%20and%20veggies%20off%20the%20stove%20to%20rest.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ENext%2C%20I%20finally%20started%20assembling%20the%20sandwich.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223611%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Lara%20uses%20tongs%20to%20pick%20up%20the%20steak%20on%20a%20plate.%20On%20another%20plate%2C%20the%20bread%20is%20laid%20out%20with%20the%20arugula%20and%20onions.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F664ba2a69fc063e829b2fc32%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222708%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ELara%20Walsh%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20brushed%20the%20sandwich%20with%20the%20mayo%20mixture%2C%20added%20a%20layer%20of%20peppery%20arugula%20and%20crunchy%20lettuce%2C%20and%20seasoned%20it%20with%20salt%20and%20pepper%2C%20per%20Ramsay's%20suggestion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20that%2C%20I%20cut%20the%20steak%20against%20the%20grain%20and%20was%20pleased%20to%20see%20that%20although%20it%20wasn't%20as%20pink%20as%20I%20normally%20liked%2C%20it%20wasn't%20dry%2C%20either.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrying%20Ramsay's%20layering%20method%2C%20I%20drizzled%20more%20sauce%2C%20added%20the%20whole%20portobello%20mushrooms%2C%20and%20then%20put%20the%20sliced%20steak%20on%20top%20of%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20drizzle%20of%20sauce%20and%20some%20sprinkles%20of%20blue%20cheese%20later%2C%20I%20was%20ready%20to%20put%20the%20top%20of%20the%20sandwich%20on%20and%20cut%20it%20in%20half%20to%20serve.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20sandwich%20was%20delicious%2C%20but%20getting%20all%20the%20different%20layers%20in%20each%20bite%20was%20hard.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223611%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Lara's%20hands%20hold%20half%20of%20the%20steak%20sandwich%20up%20while%20the%20other%2