%20but%20hit%20clerical%20work%20hardest%2C%20Australia's%20government%20predicts%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225976%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Independent%20Shellfishermen's%20Co-operative%20(ISC)%20Company%20Secretary%2C%20Joanne%20Ackers%2C%20completes%20export%20paperwork%20for%20an%20order%20at%20Bridlington%20Harbour%20in%20Bridlington%2C%20England%2C%20on%20January%2031%2C%202025.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F689db3edcfc04e97619b655f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223984%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAn%20Australian%20government%20report%20projects%20that%20generative%20AI%20will%20automate%20many%20clerical%20jobs%20and%20transform%20high-skill%20roles%20by%202050.%3Cp%3EIan%20Forsyth%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EClerical%20and%20admin%20jobs%20face%20the%20highest%20automation%20risk%20from%20generative%20AI%2C%20a%20jobs%20report%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBut%20high-skill%20roles%20are%20likely%20to%20be%20augmented%20by%202050%2C%20Jobs%20and%20Skills%20Australia%20found.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20government%20agency%20called%20for%20targeted%20training%20so%20all%20Australians%20can%20benefit%20from%20the%20AI%20shift.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAustralia's%20jobs%20market%20is%20bracing%20for%20an%20AI%20shake-up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgenerative-ai-evolution-software-companies-develop-ai-agents-workforce-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EGenerative%20AI%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20set%20to%20automate%20large%20chunks%20of%20routine%20clerical%20and%20administrative%20work%20while%20serving%20as%20a%20powerful%20assistant%20for%20high-skilled%20roles%2C%20according%20to%20new%20modelling%20from%20Jobs%20and%20Skills%20Australia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20agency's%20%26quot%3BOur%20Gen%20AI%20transition%26quot%3B%20report%2C%20released%20on%20Thursday%2C%20used%20economy-wide%20Computable%20General%20Equilibrium%20modelling%20%E2%80%94%20a%20type%20of%20economic%20simulation%20that%20tracks%20how%20changes%20ripple%20across%20all%20industries%20and%20occupations%20%E2%80%94%20to%20forecast%20how%20automation%20and%20augmentation%20could%20reshape%20Australia's%20labor%20market%20between%20now%20and%202050.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20model%20incorporated%20%26quot%3Bexposure%26quot%3B%20scores%20for%20998%20occupations%2C%20estimating%20how%20much%20of%20each%20job%20could%20be%20fully%20automated%20or%20partially%20augmented%20by%20AI%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20results%20showed%20that%20only%20about%204%25%20of%20the%20workforce%20is%20in%20occupations%20with%20high%20automation%20exposure%2C%20while%2079%25%20have%20low%20automation%20exposure%20but%20medium-to-high%20augmentation%20potential.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20means%20AI%20is%20more%20likely%20to%20change%20how%20most%20jobs%20are%20done%20rather%20than%20eliminate%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJSA's%20report%20listed%20routine%20clerical%20roles%2C%20including%20general%20clerks%2C%20receptionists%2C%20accounting%20clerks%2C%20and%20bookkeepers%2C%20as%20the%20most%20automatable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20other%20end%20of%20the%20spectrum%2C%20knowledge-intensive%20jobs%20like%20managers%2C%20engineers%2C%20healthcare%20professionals%2C%20and%20educators%20had%20higher%20augmentation%20potential.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJSA's%20modelling%20projected%20the%20biggest%20job%20declines%20by%202050%20for%20general%20clerks%2C%20receptionists%2C%20accounting%20clerks%20and%20bookkeepers%2C%20sales%20and%20marketing%20professionals%2C%20and%20programmers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20predicted%20the%20largest%20job%20gains%20for%20cleaners%20and%20laundry%20workers%2C%20nurses%20and%20midwives%2C%20business%20administration%20managers%2C%20construction%20and%20mining%20laborers%2C%20and%20hospitality%20workers%20%E2%80%94%20occupations%20that%20require%20physical%20presence%20and%20human%20touch.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20pace%20of%20change%20will%20vary%20depending%20on%20how%20quickly%20industries%20and%20occupations%20adopt%20generative%20AI%2C%20JSA%20forecasts%20slower%20employment%20growth%20through%20the%202030s%20as%20the%20labor%20market%20adjusts%2C%20followed%20by%20faster%20growth%20in%20the%202040s.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20quality%20of%20adoption%20and%20implementation%20will%20be%20instrumental%20in%20achieving%20the%20benefits%20of%20labor-augmenting%20tools%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20also%20found%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eno%20evidence%20of%20a%20broad%20decline%20in%20entry-level%20hiring%20so%20far%2C%20but%20said%20early%20signs%20suggest%20these%20jobs%20may%20evolve%2C%20shifting%20from%20performing%20repetitive%20tasks%20to%20overseeing%20and%20refining%20AI-generated%20outputs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJSA%20urged%20policymakers%20to%20prepare%20now%20with%20targeted%20training%2C%20industry%20partnerships%2C%20and%20digital%20inclusion%20efforts%20to%20ensure%20all%20workers%20can%20benefit%20from%20the%20AI%20transition%2C%20especially%20women%2C%20older%20Australians%2C%20First%20Nations%20peoples%2C%20and%20people%20with%20disabilities%2C%20who%20the%20report%20found%20are%20more%20likely%20to%20be%20in%20roles%20with%20higher%20automation%20risk.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220c3352eb-bb8a-4df9-b61e-3d4412992e6d%5C%22%3EExperts%20are%20split%20over%20how%20AI%20will%20affect%20employment%20%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20findings%20come%20amid%20a%20wider%20debate%20over%20how%20AI%20will%20affect%20human%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESatya%20Nadella%2C%20the%20Microsoft%20CEO%2C%20has%20argued%20that%20while%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrosoft-ceo-satya-nadella-knowledge-work-evolution-ai-agents-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eknowledge%20work%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20will%20be%20redefined%20as%20AI%20takes%20on%20tasks%20once%20done%20exclusively%20by