wilder%25252520sleeper%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJoybird%20Wilder%20Sleeper%20Sectional%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20specifically%2C%20is%20the%20closest%20sleeper%20I've%20seen%20akin%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Frh-cloud-couch-dupes%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECloud%20couch%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20with%20overstuffed%20cushions%2C%20a%20deep%2C%20inviting%20seat%2C%20clean%20lines%2C%20and%20a%20cozy%20chaise%20to%20lounge%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20decided%20on%20a%20dreamy%20aqua%20color%20that%20is%20pet-friendly%2C%20and%20stain-%20and%20water-resistant.%20Once%20it%20was%20in%20place%20(with%20in-home%20setup%20for%20extra%20ease)%2C%20it%20immediately%20brightened%20my%20entire%20living%20room%2C%20a%20far%20cry%20from%20my%20previously%20drab%20gray%20sofa.%20It's%20also%20big%20and%20really%20commands%20the%20space.%20I%20just%20have%20one%20small%20problem%3A%20it%20dwarfs%20my%20existing%20furniture%2C%20making%20me%20want%20to%20redecorate%20everything%E2%80%A6from%20sizing%20up%20my%20area%20rug%20to%20investing%20in%20an%20end%20table%20that%20looks%20more%20proportionate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20been%20living%2C%20er%2C%20lounging%2C%20with%20my%20Joybird%20sofa%20for%20about%20three%20months%20now.%20I'll%20get%20into%20more%20details%20about%20the%20design%20and%20available%20customizations%2C%20comfort%2C%20durability%2C%20and%20what%20it's%20like%20to%20spend%20a%20few%20nights%20sleeping%20on%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2257551690-478b-4aed-b016-717ef52b4fd4%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Design%20and%20customizations%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EDesign%20and%20customizations%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225712%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22aqua%20blue%20joybird%20sleeper%20sofa%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F689248f9f748d8c055f6ebef%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20roomy%20Joybird%20Sleeper%20Sofa%20is%20available%20in%2078%20fabrics%20and%20pulls%20out%20into%20a%20queen%20size%20bed.%3Cp%3EJaclyn%20Turner%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThanks%20to%20its%20boxy%20profile%20and%20removable%20pillows%2C%20the%20Wilder%20reminds%20me%20of%20an%20RH%20Cloud%20Couch%2C%20but%20in%20sofa%20bed%20form.%20The%20cushions%20are%20deep%20and%20plush%2C%20with%20detached%20pillows%20that%20line%20the%20back%20and%20sides.%20It%20is%20both%20timeless%20and%20contemporary.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20sofa%20measures%20123%20inches%2C%20which%20is%20over%2010%20feet%20long.%20The%20main%20frame%20houses%20a%20queen-size%20pull-out%20with%20a%20deep-seated%20attached%20sectional.%20It's%20definitely%20one%20of%20the%20largest%20sleeper%20sectionals%20Joybird%20offers.%20If%20you%20like%20the%20look%20of%20the%20Wilder%20but%20it's%20too%20big%20for%20your%20space%2C%20Joybird%20also%20offers%20a%20%3Ca%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3D8c0b0828663eadb4fa134f95f85cd96212c8a6d378d95b8f4842c59f3e377c75%26postID%3D68923d0db04eda2658c77645%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fhome%252Fjoybird-sleeper-sofa-review%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fjoybird.com%252Fsleeper-twins%252Fwilder-sleeper-twin%252F%253Ffabric%253Dkey-largo-zenith-teal%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etwin-size%20love%20seat%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20is%20much%20more%20small-space%20friendly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Wilder%20Sectional%20can%20be%20oriented%20with%20the%20chaise%20on%20either%20the%20right%20or%20the%20left%20side%2C%20but%20it%20is%20not%20reversible%20down%20the%20road.%20A%20missed%20opportunity%20within%20the%20design%20is%20storage%20carved%20out%20within%20the%20sectional%2C%20as%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3D2b19d55f24a0cdde114ccb88decca4007bf12242eee6dec149cf965fb1003de4%26postID%3D68923d0db04eda2658c77645%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fhome%252Fjoybird-sleeper-sofa-review%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.jdoqocy.com%252Fclick-6415797-15906776%253Furl%253Dhttps%25253A%25252F%25252Fjoybird.com%25252Fsecti%255B%25E2%2580%25A6%255Ds%25252Fbriar-sleeper-storage-sectional%25252F%25253Ffabric%25253Dessence-ash%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBriar%20sleeper%20sectional%3C%2Fa%3E%20does%20have%20built-in%20storage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJoybird%20offers%20two%204.5-inch%20mattress%20options%3A%20a%20standard%20foam%20mattress%20with%20a%20pressure-relieving%20medium%20feel%20or%20the%20Tempur-Response%20Memory%20foam%20upgrade%2C%20which%20combines%20high-density%20foam%20and%20memory%20foam%20for%20more%20support.%20I%20chose%20the%20Tempur%20upgrade.%20Whichever%20mattress%20you%20choose%2C%20you'll%20get%20something%20thinner%20and%20shorter%20than%20a%20standard%20queen-sized%20mattress.%20It%20could%20be%20worth%20considering%20specially%20sized%20sheets%20if%20you're%20concerned%20about%20a%20standard%20fitted%20sheet%20being%20too%20baggy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20sofa's%20construction%20details%20include%20an%20engineered%20wood%20frame%20consisting%20of%20an%20assembly%20reinforced%20with%20corner%20blocking%20and%20kiln-dried%20solid%20wood%20spring%20rails%20for%20warping%20prevention.%20The%20bench%20seat%20cushions%20have%20a%20high-density%20polyurethane%20foam%20core%20and%20are%20not%20reversible.%20The%20joints%20are%20glued%2C%20reinforced%2C%20and%20stapled%20to%20ensure%20frame%20stability%20and%20longevity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJoybird%20offers%2078%20upholstery%20options%20and%20groups%20them%20by%20velvet%2C%20pet-friendly%2C%20safeguard%20(stain-resistant%20or%20performance)%2C%20sustainable%20(made%20with%20recycled%20fibers)%2C%20and%20Greenguard-Gold%20certified.%20On%20the%20website%2C%20you%20can%20filter%20by%20all%20those%20preferences%20or%20by%20a%20color%20grouping.%20There%20are%20tons%20of%20options.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20took%20home%20a%20few%20samples%20to%20see%20how%20the%20fabric%20looked%20in%20my%20space%2C%20but%20you%20can%20also%20order%20free%20swatches%20if%20you%20don't%20live%20near%20one%20of%20the%20Joybird's%2013%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3Ddf17876fc6c7ce852b53e135d41fe55980a711d7d697de584d90645ac9130f6c%26postID%3D68923d0db04eda2658c77645%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fhome%252Fjoybird-sleeper-sofa-review%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fjoybird.com%252Fshowrooms%252F%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eshowrooms%3C%2Fa%3E.%20A%20feature%20that%20I%20loved%20during%20the%20decision%20process%20is%20that%20Joybird%20has%20an%20AR%20plug-in%20that%20lets%20you%20view%20your%20chosen%20sofa%20and%20see%20how%20it%20will%20virtually%20fit%20in%20your%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222622%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22AR%20image%20of%20a%20sofa%20on%20top%20of%20where%20it%20would%20go%20in%20the%20room%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68924402f748d8c055f6eb47%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221206%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20used%20the%20AR%20tool%20to%20visualize%20how%20the%20sofa%20would%20look%20in%20my%20space.%20I%20thought%20it%20was%20pretty%20accurate.%3Cp%3EJaclyn%20Turner%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20settled%20on%20a%20performance%20Sunbrella%20fabric%20called%20Premier%20Sea%2C%20a%20light%20turquoise%20twill%20weave%20that%20is%20water-%20and%20stain-resistant%20and%20pet-friendly.%20It's%20slightly%20textured%20but%20still%20soft.%20After%20I%20ran%20a%20few%20drops%20of%20water%20over%20my%20swatch%20and%20the%20liquid%20rolled%20off%2C%20I%20was%20convinced.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d7f35610-1adf-4baa-a846-c01e6802cae1%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Delivery%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EDelivery%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224330%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22men%20carrying%20a%20sofa%20up%20a%20landing%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6892451385e81483682f522f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223247%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIn-home%20setup%20ensures%20I%20didn't%20have%20to%20lift%20a%20finger.%20The%20delivery%20crew%20masterfully%20navigated%20the%20sofa%20up%20a%20flight%20of%20stairs%20and%20through%20my%20tiny%20landing.%3Cp%3EJaclyn%20Turner%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EJoybird's%20sofas%20are%20made%20to%20order%20in%20Tijuana%2C%20Mexico%2C%20and%20then%20transferred%20to%20San%20Diego%20to%20be%20shipped%20across%20the%20country.%20The%20process%20takes%20four%20to%20six%20weeks.%20Joybird's%20sofas%20qualify%20for%20premium%20in-home%20delivery%2C%20which%20costs%20%24179.%20Despite%20the%20extra%20cost%2C%20in-home%20delivery%20is%20well%20worth%20it%20because%20this%20couch%20is%20heavy%20and%20bulky%20to%20move%20on%20your%20own.%20The%20truck's%20manifest%20says%20the%20sleeper%20weighed%20253%20pounds%20and%20the%20chaise%20sectional%20147%20pounds.%20Honestly%2C%20I%20can't%20imagine%20what%20will%20happen%20when%20it%20comes%20time%20to%20move.%20I%20took%20notes%20as%20the%20two%20delivery%20drivers%20shimmied%20it%20up%20a%20flight%20of%20stairs%20to%20my%20small%20landing%20and%20through%20my%20single%20front%20door.%20I%20was%20nervous%20that%20I%20had%20chosen%20a%20sofa%20too%20wide%20to%20fit%20through%20the%20threshold.%20Fortunately%2C%20it%20fit%2C%20but%20by%20a%20hair.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20it%20was%20in%20place%20in%20my%20living%20room%2C%20a%20hidden%20bracket%20kept%20the%20two%20pieces%20together.%20The%20crew%20also%20arranged%20the%20sofa's%20many%20pillows%2C%20which%20were%20bagged%20separately.%20The%20mattress%20was%20in%20place%20within%20the%20sleeper%20mechanism%20but%20wrapped%20in%20plastic.%20It%20needed%20some%20time%20to%20off-gas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20process%20was%20pretty%20fast%2C%20and%20the%20crew%20took%20all%20the%20wrappings%20and%20garbage.%20By%20the%20time%20I%20thanked%20them%20and%20shut%20the%20door%20to%20let%20them%20out%2C%20my%20dog%20had%20already%20found%20the%20opportunity%20to%20give%20it%20a%20test%20sit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c0a75c6e-197a-4c1e-a062-cd604de1e368%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Comfort%5C%22%3EComfort%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22detail%20shots%20side%20by%20side%20of%20the%20joybird%20sleeper%20sofa%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F689248f9f748d8c055f6ebee%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Joybird%20is%20extremely%20comfortable%2C%20the%20perfect%20place%20to%20curl%20up%2C%20watch%20movies%20and%20read%20magazines.%3Cp%3EJaclyn%20Turner%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Wilder%20Sofa%20seats%20are%20firm%20without%20being%20uncomfortable.%20There's%20no%20sinking%20in%20or%20dipping%20down%3B%20I%20feel%20well-supported.%20The%20back%20cushions%20are%20overstuffed%20and%20plush%2C%20waiting%20to%20be%20curled%20up%20against.%20This%20couch%20is%20made%20for%20lounging%3B%20it's%20definitely%20large%20enough%20for%20two%20adults%20to%20sprawl%20out%2C%20but%20could%20easily%20seat%20four%20people%20comfortably.%20The%20deep-seated%20nature%20takes%20some%20getting%20used%20to%2C%20as%20my%20feet%20don't%20reach%20the%20floor%20when%20I%20lean%20up%20against%20the%20cushions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d29f1292-1fb2-444c-892b-55dcb79ab8f7%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Sleeping%20on%20the%20Wilder%5C%22%3ESleeping%20on%20the%20Wilder%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225712%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22sofa%20bed%20opened%20with%20pilows%20off%20to%20the%20side%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68924402f748d8c055f6eb48%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20queen-size%20Tempur-Response%20Memory%20foam%20was%20surprisingly%20comfortable%20to%20sleep%20on%20%E2%80%94%20a%20good%20medium-firm%20that%20slept%20cool%2C%20but%20it%20wasn't%20very%20good%20at%20isolating%20motion.%3Cp%3EJaclyn%20Turner%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20came%20time%20to%20convert%20the%20Wilder%20into%20a%20bed%2C%20I%20was%20thankful%20for%20the%20sectional%20portion%2C%20which%20I%20could%20pile%20all%20the%20loose%20pillows%20on%20top%20of.%20Removing%20the%20bench%20cushion%20reveals%20the%20pull-out%20bed%20underneath.%20The%20long%20cushion%20is%20large%20and%20unwieldy%2C%20but%20it%20was%20still%20manageable%20to%20lift.%20If%20you%20have%20mobility%20issues%2C%20opt%20for%20a%20sofa%20with%20a%20split%20cushion%20design%2C%20which%20will%20be%20lighter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20pull-out%20bed%20easily%20glides%20out%2C%20and%20I%20can%20do%20it%20swiftly%20with%20one%20hand.%20To%20create%20a%20headboard%2C%20I%20stick%20the%20bench%20cushion%20in%20the%20gap%20between%20the%20mattress%20and%20the%20sofa%2C%20which%20also%20keeps%20me%20from%20having%20to%20leave%20the%20cushion%20on%20the%20floor%20or%20propped%20against%20the%20wall.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22side%20by%20side%20of%20a%20weight%20on%20a%20sofa%20bed%20mattress%20and%20the%20mechanism%20to%20pull%20out%20the%20sofa%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F689248f985e81483682f52a0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDespite%20being%20just%204.5%20inches%20thick%2C%20the%20high%20density%20Tempur-foam%20doesn't%20sink%20much%2C%20as%20demonstrated%20by%20the%2020%20pound%20weight%2C%20meaning%20you%20won't%20feel%20like%20you're%20bottoming%20out%20or%20notice%20the%20support%20bar.%20The%20bed%20easily%20pulls%20out.%3Cp%3EJaclyn%20Turner%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20a%20small%20gap%20between%20the%20sofa's%20edge%20and%20the%20sofa%20bed%20to%20keep%20the%20mattress%20to%20the%20standard%2060-inch%20width%20of%20a%20queen.%20At%2072%20inches%20long%2C%20it's%20shorter%20than%20a%20standard%20queen-size%20bed%20(which%20is%20usually%2080%20inches%20long%20by%2060%20inches%20wide)%2C%20but%20not%20atypical%20for%20a%20sleeper%20sofa%20mattress%2C%20as%20other%20brands%20like%20Interior%20Define%20and%20West%20Elm%20list%20their%20mattresses%20as%20being%20similarly%20sized.%20Based%20on%20where%20I%20placed%20my%20pillow%2C%20my%20feet%20sometimes%20stuck%20off%20the%20bed%2C%20depending%20on%20how%20I%20lay.%20I'm%20about%20five-feet-five-inches.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20never%20thought%20I'd%20see%20the%20day%20when%20I%20had%20a%20good%20night's%20rest%20on%20a%20sofa%20bed%2C%20but%20I%20awoke%20with%20no%20aches%20or%20pains%20from%20the%20bed.%20It's%20a%20firm%20mattress%20that%20didn't%20make%20me%20feel%20like%20I%20was%20sinking%20into%20too%20soft%20foam.%20I%20also%20couldn't%20feel%20the%20support%20bar%20as%20I%20slept%2C%20which%20is%20a%20common%20complaint%20for%20sleeper%20sofas.%20The%20mattress%20was%20also%20remarkably%20cool.%20It%20was%20very%20comfortable%20to%20sit%20on%20the%20edges%20of%20the%20mattress%2C%20which%20is%20good%20if%20you%20share%20the%20bed%20with%20a%20partner%20and%20need%20to%20make%20use%20of%20all%20the%20allowable%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20one%20drawback%20was%20that%20I%20could%20feel%20movement%20whenever%20my%20dog%20moved.%20He%20was%20unfamiliar%20with%20the%20new%20bed%20and%20spent%20a%20fair%20amount%20of%20time%20trying%20to%20find%20his%20comfy%20spot%2C%20and%20I%20felt%20every%20readjustment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDue%20to%20the%20sofa's%20large%20size%2C%20you%20may%20even%20find%20that%20you%20don't%20need%20to%20convert%20the%20sofa%20to%20a%20sleeper%20if%20just%20one%20person%20is%20sleeping.%20The%20roomy%20bench%20cushion%20itself%20is%20easily%20the%20dimensions%20of%20a%20twin%2C%20and%20this%20bed%20sleeps%20three%2C%20if%20you%20take%20the%20long%20bench%20cushion%20and%20find%20a%20place%20to%20put%20it%20on%20the%20floor.%20Regardless%2C%20it's%20well-sized%20for%20afternoon%20naps%2C%20and%20definitely%20comfortable%20enough%20for%20it%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222d5a132f-23cf-414f-8284-4ce12d1a7378%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Durability%5C%22%3EDurability%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20sofa%20feels%20well-built.%20The%20two%20pieces%20connected%20together%20haven't%20shifted%2C%20and%20the%20sofa-bed%20mechanism%20operates%20smoothly%2C%20with%20no%20creaks%20or%20whines.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20upholstery%20you%20choose%20will%20ultimately%20affect%20the%20overall%20longevity%20of%20your%20sofa.%20The%20Sunbrella%20fabric%20resists%20water%2C%20but%20due%20to%20its%20soft%20nature%2C%20I've%20noticed%20some%20light%20fuzziness%20along%20the%20edges%20of%20the%20bench%20cushion%20(where%20pants%20and%20legs%20rub%20up%20on%20the%20fabric%2C%20creating%20friction).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20fabric%20repels%20liquids%20and%20stains%2C%20and%20resists%20any%20snags%20from%20my%20dog's%20nails.%20I've%20truly%20%26quot%3Blived%26quot%3B%20on%20this%20sofa%2C%20and%20haven't%20treated%20it%20particularly%20delicately.%20After%20a%20few%20months%20of%20daily%20use%2C%20the%20cushions%20show%20no%20signs%20of%20sagging%20or%20wear%20and%20tear.%20It%20still%20looks%20brand%20new.%20I%20have%20no%20qualms%20about%20this%20sofa%20serving%20me%20for%20years%20to%20come.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2230c5a4bc-0ff8-47b0-9e29-04aa7e0f8b80%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Cons%20to%20consider%5C%22%3ECons%20to%20consider%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225712%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22ripples%20in%20the%20upholstery%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F689248f93d5881a51c1ea470%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20fabric%20ripples%20a%20bit%2C%20which%20creates%20a%20lived-in%20look.%20I%20think%20the%20light%20color%20amplifies%20it%20more.%3Cp%3EJaclyn%20Turner%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20first%20got%20the%20couch%2C%20I%20noticed%20that%20the%20bench%20cushion%20seat%20inched%20forward%20throughout%20the%20day.%20I%20inconveniently%20had%20to%20readjust%20the%20heavy%20pillow%20every%20day.%20I%20voiced%20my%20concern%20to%20Joybird%2C%20who%20swiftly%20remedied%20the%20issue%20with%20a%20non-slip%20cushion%20pad%20that%20I%20placed%20between%20the%20bench%20seat%20and%20the%20sofa%20frame%3B%20I%20now%20readjust%20the%20seat%20far%20less%20often.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20sofa%20is%20also%20very%20deep.%20I'm%20most%20comfortable%20lounging%20or%20sitting%20far%20back%20and%20letting%20my%20feet%20dangle.%20You'll%20have%20to%20take%20a%20big%20scooch%20back%20or%20forget%20about%20leaning%20against%20the%20cushions%20if%20you%20want%20your%20feet%20to%20touch%20the%20ground.%20This%20is%20less%20of%20a%20con%20and%20more%20of%20a%20caveat%20of%20deep-seated%20sofas%20and%20how%20you%20want%20to%20sit%20on%20your%20sofa.%20But%20the%20%26quot%3Bissue%26quot%3B%20was%20amplified%20by%20my%20older%20parents%2C%20who%20didn't%20love%20having%20to%20adjust%20themselves%20to%20get%20comfortable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20eagle-eyed%20mother%20also%20noted%20that%20the%20seat%20fabric%20looked%20wrinkled%20around%20the%20edges.%20It%20doesn't%20bother%20me%20%E2%80%94%20these%20ripples%20give%20it%20a%20lived-in%20look%20%E2%80%94%20and%20is%20likely%20most%20noticeable%20due%20to%20the%20light%20color%20I%20chose.%20I%20think%20it's%20the%20way%20the%20fabric%20drapes%2C%20but%20it%20seems%20there%20is%20some%20excess.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2232116e1a-3538-4b80-aa10-e154f096b336%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22What%20are%20the%20alternatives%3F%5C%22%3EWhat%20are%20the%20alternatives%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%2