0can%20create%20porn%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Marina%20Adshade%2C%20a%20sex%20economist%20and%20assistant%20professor%20at%20the%20University%20of%20British%20Columbia.%20%26quot%3BThe%20real%20money%20is%20being%20made%20in%20the%20distribution.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdshade%20referenced%20the%20popular%20adult%20website%20Pornhub's%20market%20dominance.%20The%20company%20is%20privately%20held%20and%20does%20not%20report%20annual%20revenue%3B%20its%20parent%20company%20MindGeek%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3D11b08aa67cbcdb86e60f37e9dd93ea5a53ee853c3e3fbfc060aecf0d83310dd5%26postID%3D6894af41dc525dd064c2c45d%26postSlug%3Delon-musk-grok-nsfw-ai-spicy-content-potential-revenue-risk-2025-8%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.morningbrew.com%252Fstories%252F2-execs-from-pornhubs-parent-company-mindgeek-resign%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20%24460%20million%20in%20revenue%20in%202018%20before%20its%20acquisition%20by%20Ethical%20Capital%20Partners.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnlyFans%2C%20another%20major%20player%20in%20the%20adult%20entertainment%20market%2C%20reported%20%246.6%20billion%20in%20gross%20payments%20to%20creators%20in%202023%2C%20of%20which%20the%20company%20takes%20a%2020%25%20cut.%20Its%20owner%2C%20Fenix%20International%20Limited%2C%20reported%20net%20revenue%20of%20%241.31%20billion%20for%20the%20year.%20(Twitter%2C%20before%20Musk%20acquired%20it%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theverge.com%2F23327809%2Ftwitter-onlyfans-child-sexual-content-problem-elon-musk%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereportedly%3C%2Fa%3E%20explored%20monetizing%20adult%20content%20before%20nixing%20the%20idea%20after%20its%20Red%20Team%20concluded%20in%20April%202022%20that%20the%20platform%20%26quot%3Bcannot%20accurately%20detect%20child%20sexual%20exploitation%20and%20non-consensual%20nudity%20at%20scale.%26quot%3B)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECustomizability%20could%20prove%20to%20be%20xAI's%20edge.%20Adshade%20said%20that%20AI-generated%20porn%20can%20cheaply%20serve%20any%20user's%20specific%20preferences%2C%20giving%20it%20a%20market%20advantage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat's%20where%20the%20money%20is%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20plenty%20of%20existing%20demand%20for%20AI-generated%20sexual%20images%2C%20much%20of%20which%20has%20funneled%20to%20gray-market%20tools.%20Analysis%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findicator.media%2Fp%2Fai-nudifiers-continue-to-reach-millions-and-make-millions%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIndicator%3C%2Fa%3E%20estimates%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fadvertisers-left-x-crypto-ai-undressing-apps-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI%20%26quot%3Bnudifier%26quot%3B%20tools%3C%2Fa%3E%20make%20around%20%2436%20million%20a%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHenry%20Ajder%20watched%20these%20tools%20grow.%20He%20advises%20companies%20like%20Meta%2C%20Adobe%2C%20and%20EY%20on%20deepfakes%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eand%20their%20impact.%20He%20described%20a%20network%20of%20tools%20that%20masquerade%20on%20the%20App%20Store%20as%20%26quot%3Bfun%2C%20meme-ifying%20apps%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20advertise%20themselves%20as%20deepfake%20tools%20on%20other%20platforms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20xAI%20is%20one%20of%20the%20first%20big%20players%20to%20tap%20into%20that%20demand%2C%20Ajder%20said%2C%20though%20the%20company's%20offerings%20remain%20%26quot%3Bsoftcore.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20something%20that%20a%20lot%20of%20the%20other%20models%20don't%20allow%20you%20to%20generate%2C%26quot%3B%20Ajder%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20guess%20it's%20trying%20to%20cater%20to%20an%20audience%2C%20and%20seeing%20a%20gap%20in%20the%20market.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOpenAI%20CEO%20Sam%20Altman%20recently%20acknowledged%20that%20NSFW%20AI%20may%20cause%20users%20to%20spend%20more%20time%20on%20platforms%20that%20offer%20it.%20On%20Cleo%20Abram's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DhmtuvNfytjM%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EYouTube%20show%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20he%20said%20that%20adding%20a%20sex-bot%20could%20%26quot%3Bjuice%20growth%20or%20revenue%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20that%20he%20has%20abstained%20because%20it%20doesn't%20align%20with%20OpenAI's%20mission.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EApp%20download%20data%20from%20market%20intelligence%20firm%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fsensortower.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESensor%20Tower%3C%2Fa%3E%20suggests%20some%20of%20the%20new%20Grok%20features%20may%20have%20boosted%20downloads.%20The%20week%20xAI%20added%20companions%20%E2%80%94%20a%20week%20after%20the%20new%20Grok-4%20model%20debuted%20%E2%80%94%20global%20downloads%20increased%20an%20estimated%2041%25.%20The%20week%20it%20added%20%26quot%3Bspicy%26quot%3B%20video%20generation%2C%20global%20downloads%20fell%20an%20estimated%209%25%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0but%20US%20downloads%20increased%20by%2033%25%2C%20per%20Sensor%20Tower.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThose%20looking%20to%20chat%20with%20the%20AI%20companion%20Ani%20or%20generate%20an%20NSFW%20video%20with%20Grok%20Imagine%20will%20have%20to%20pay.%20For%20premium%20access%2C%20xAI%20charges%20%2430%2Fmonth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EXAI%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222820b767-8600-477c-8426-91c76ee4cfb3%5C%22%3ENSFW%20chatbots%20pose%20brand%20risks%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20all%20the%20money%20that%20xAI's%20adult%20turn%20could%20bring%20in%2C%20it%20comes%20with%20risks%20and%20moderation%20challenges.%20Like%20other%20AI%20companies%2C%20xAI%20will%20need%20to%20ensure%20its%20AI%20models%20are%20properly%20trained%20to%20prevent%20outputting%20illegal%20content.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGrok's%20%26quot%3Bspicy%26quot%3B%20video%20generation%20is%20only%20available%20for%20AI-generated%20images.%20When%20a%20user%20uploads%20their%20own%20image%20to%20the%20video%20generator%2C%20the%20only%20options%20are%20%26quot%3Bfun%2C%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3Bnormal%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bcustom.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20tried%20to%20test%20the%20limits%20of%20the%20%26quot%3Bcustom%26quot%3B%20button%20to%20see%20how%20it%20compared%20to%20%26quot%3Bspicy%26quot%3B%20mode.%20While%20it%20was%20willing%20to%20comply%20with%20my%20prompt%20to%20%26quot%3Btake%20off%20shirt%26quot%3B%20on%20a%20photo%20of%20myself%20I%20had%20uploaded%2C%20I%20was%20unable%20to%20convince%20the%20AI%20to%20remove%20my%20pants.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20tried%20multiple%20times%20to%20have%20the%20bot%20create%20NSFW%20videos%20of%20celebrities.%20While%20my%20attempts%20to%20make%20%26quot%3Bspicy%26quot%3B%20videos%20of%20Taylor%20Swift%20were%20shut%20down%20by%20Grok%2C%20the%20tool%20easily%20allowed%20me%20to%20create%20NSFW%20videos%20of%20other%20celebrities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20could%20lead%20to%20PR%20headaches.%20Celebrities%20could%20publicly%20criticize%20xAI%20over%20deepfakes%20with%20their%20likeness%2C%20especially%20any%20containing%20nudity%2C%20and%20they%20command%20large%20fan%20bases.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELegal%20recourse%20around%20deepfakes%20isn't%20cut-and-dried%20and%20continues%20to%20evolve.%20The%20recently%20enacted%20Take%20It%20Down%20Act%20protects%20victims%20of%20deepfakes%2C%20but%20images%20of%20non-minors%20must%20include%20specific%20sexual%20body%20parts%20to%20be%20subject%20to%20the%20legislation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20states%20have%20more%20stringent%20laws%20on%20AI-generated%20deepfakes%2C%20and%20those%20affected%20could%20also%20file%20civil%20claims.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-is-section-230-internet-law-communications-decency-act-explained-2020-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESection%20230%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20Communications%20Decency%20Act%20of%201996%20largely%20protects%20online%20platforms%20from%20liability%20for%20content%20shared%20by%20users.%3C%2