er%2C%20and%20waiting%20an%20inordinate%20amount%20of%20time%20waiting%20to%20use%20the%20bathroom%20was%20expected.%20Ask%20anyone%20in%20this%20type%20of%20household%2C%20someone%20is%20always%20waiting%20to%20use%20the%20bathroom.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20our%20house%20was%20just%20one%20of%20millions%20of%20families%20living%20with%20their%20parents%20and%20adult%20children%2C%20cousins%2C%20brothers%20and%20sisters%2C%20or%20grandparents%20and%20their%20grandchildren.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pewresearch.org%2Fsocial-trends%2F2022%2F03%2F24%2Ffinancial-issues-top-the-list-of-reasons-u-s-adults-live-in-multigenerational-homes%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPew%20Research%20Center%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20there%20were%2059.7%20million%20U.S.%20residents%20who%20lived%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmillennials-living-with-parents-multigenerational-households-financial-benefits-2022-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emultiple%20generations%20under%20the%20same%20roof%20%3C%2Fa%3Eas%20of%20March%202021%20%E2%80%94%20a%20number%20that%20has%20quadrupled%20since%201971.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a7cfe3f4-c490-4147-86b6-6e38cbe9fa81%5C%22%3EI've%20tried%20to%20live%20alone%2C%20but%20it%20never%20lasted%20long%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%2020-something%20in%20the%20aughts%2C%20I%20was%20so%20excited%20to%20be%20in%20my%20very%20own%20apartment.%20But%20then%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwoman-warned-great-recession-2008-brooksley-born-wall-street-sexism-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EGreat%20Recession%20of%202007%20%3C%2Fa%3Ehappened%2C%20and%20I%20was%20right%20back%20under%20my%20mother's%20roof%20along%20with%20my%20brother%20and%20a%20family%20friend%20who%20had%20been%20couch%20surfing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20here%20I%20am%20many%20years%20later%2C%20living%20in%20yet%20another%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business