%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EVanguard%3C%2Fa%3E%20survey%20of%201%2C011%20respondents%20published%20in%20March%2C%20at%20least%2057%25%20of%20Americans%20are%20earning%20less%20than%203%25%20a%20year%20on%20their%20cash%20savings.%20Eight%20percent%20said%20they%20have%20their%20savings%20in%20physical%20cash%2C%20meaning%20they're%20yielding%20nothing%3B%2016%25%20are%20earning%20less%20than%201%25%3B%20and%2033%25%20are%20earning%201%25-3%25.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20suggests%20that%20even%20if%20savers%20are%20aware%20enough%20to%20move%20their%20money%20to%20an%20account%20or%20product%20with%20a%20higher%20interest%20rate%20than%20the%20standard%20checking%20or%20savings%20account%20%E2%80%94%20the%20annual%20yield%20on%20which%20is%20under%200.5%25%20%E2%80%94%20they're%20still%20not%20capitalizing%20on%20the%20highest-yielding%20products%20on%20the%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20it's%20below%203%25%20you%20should%20be%20looking%2C%26quot%3B%20Byrne%20said.%20%26quot%3BYou%20should%20be%20finding%20a%20vehicle%20that%20has%20a%20better%20rate%20than%20that%2C%20and%20also%20has%20the%20features%20you%20need%2C%20whether%20that's%20FDIC%20insurance%20or%20the%20ability%20to%20move%20money%20seamlessly.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHigh-yield%20savings%20accounts%2C%20certificates%20of%20deposit%2C%20and%20money%20market%20rates%20can%20vary%20by%20institution%2C%20length%20of%20deposit%2C%20and%20the%20amount%20deposited.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMoney-market%20funds%2C%20which%20hold%20cash%20equivalents%20like%20ultra%20low-risk%20short-term%20Treasurys%2C%20are%20more%20liquid%20than%20other%20products%20CDs%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20often%20force%20investors%20to%20pay%20a%20penalty%20if%20they%20pull%20their%20money%20out%20before%20the%20maturity%20date.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20examples%20of%20some%20money%20market%20accounts%20%E2%80%94%20which%20you%20can%20invest%20in%20through%20a%20brokerage%20account%20with%20a%20firm%20like%20Charles%20Sc