p%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224658%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20close-up%20of%20Elon%20Musk%20looking%20to%20his%20left.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68366cedc6ad288d1482031f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223105%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EElon%20Musk%20said%20the%20time%20he%20spent%20on%20politics%20is%20%26quot%3Bless%20than%20people%20would%20think.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EChip%20Somodevilla%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20prominent%20companies%20have%20since%20followed%20Musk%20out%20of%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVC%20firm%20Andreessen%20Horowitz%20is%20the%20most%20recent%20high-profile%20company%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flist-corporations-leaving-delaware-elon-musk-spacex-tesla-dropbox-roblox-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eexit%20Delaware%3C%2Fa%3E%20because%2C%20the%20company%20said%20in%20a%20blog%20post%2C%20recent%20rulings%20by%20the%20Court%20of%20Chancery%20had%20undermined%20its%20%26quot%3Breputation%20for%20unbiased%20expertise.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECompanies%20like%20Roblox%2C%20Dropbox%2C%20and%20Trump%20Media%20have%20also%20left%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETexas%2C%20Nevada%2C%20Florida%2C%20and%20Wyoming%20have%20become%20preferred%20destinations%20for%20some%20business%20leaders%20in%20a%20shift%20that%20some%20have%20dubbed%20%26quot%3BDexit%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20reference%20to%20the%20UK's%20withdrawal%20from%20the%20European%20Union%2C%20known%20as%20Brexit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20state's%20historical%20dominance%20as%20a%20destination%20for%20companies%20to%20incorporate%20is%20rooted%20in%20the%20Delaware%20General%20Corporation%20Law%2C%20a%20business-friendly%20statute%20that%20acts%20as%20the%20bedrock%20of%20its%20corporate%20law.%20Companies%20leaving%20Delaware%20might%20do%20so%20for%20various%20reasons%2C%20including%20privacy%20or%20tax%20preferences%2C%20but%20for%20Musk%2C%20it's%20about%20finding%20greener%20legal%20pastures.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20its%20part%2C%20Delaware%20isn't%20overly%20worried.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b919c5eb-94ed-454e-b0b8-5fa7306aaeb2%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EDexit%3F%20Not%20according%20to%20Delaware.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAttorneys%20and%20state%20officials%20still%20consider%20Delaware%20the%20premier%20destination%20for%20corporations%2C%20despite%20Musk's%20criticism.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYes%2C%20there%20has%20been%20some%20political%20rhetoric%20about%20leaving%20Delaware%2C%26quot%3B%20Delaware%20Secretary%20of%20State%20Charuni%20Patibanda-Sanchez%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20our%20data%20is%20showing%20is%20that%20Delaware%20is%20still%20the%20preeminent%20place%20to%20incorporate%20your%20business.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPatibanda-Sanchez's%20office%20oversees%20the%20Division%20of%20Corporations%2C%20which%20says%20the%20state%20was%20home%20to%20over%202.1%20million%20corporations%20and%20two-thirds%20of%20Fortune%20500%20companies%20in%202024.%20Still%2C%20the%20number%20of%20business%20entities%20formed%20in%20Delaware%20has%20slowed%20slightly%2C%20falling%20from%20about%20313%2C000%20in%202022%20to%20about%20289%2C000%20in%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJoshua%20Margolin%2C%20a%20partner%20at%20Selendy%20Gay%20who%20is%20familiar%20with%20corporate%20governance%20in%20Delaware%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Etold%20Business%20Insider%20that%20the%20state's%20decadeslong%20experience%20navigating%20corporate%20disputes%20is%20a%20big%20reason%20the%20state%20remains%20a%20top%20destination.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou've%20got%20judges%20who%20sit%20on%20the%20Court%20of%20Chancery%20who%20have%20spent%20their%20entire%20careers%20litigating%20corporate%20disputes%2C%26quot%3B%20Margolin%20said.%20%26quot%3BThat%20is%20invaluable%20to%20have%20that%20experience%20on%20the%20bench%20when%20you're%20bringing%20a%20dispute%2C%20whether%20you're%20the%20plaintiff%20or%20the%20defendant.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMargolin%20added%20that%20Delaware%20has%20a%20%26quot%3Bbreadth%20and%20depth%20of%20case%20law%20and%20precedent%20that%20I%20don't%20think%20other%20states%20can%20rival.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20if%20you%20went%20back%20over%20time%2C%20you'd%20see%20various%20states%20creating%20business%20courts%20that%20are%20in%20one%20way%20or%20another%20meant%20to%20try%20to%20mirror%20the%20expertise%20of%20the%20Court%20of%20Chancery%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELindsey%20Mignano%2C%20founding%20partner%20of%20SSM%20Law%20PC%2C%20which%20represents%20emerging%20tech%20companies%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Esaid%20Delaware%20remains%20the%20%26quot%3Bsimplest%2C%20most%20cost-effective%20choice%26quot%3B%20for%20business%20founders.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMignano%20said%20many%20of%20the%20documents%20related%20to%20governing%20financing%20for%20startups%20are%20based%20on%20Delaware%20corporate%20law%2C%20meaning%20attorneys%20would%20need%20to%20adopt%20those%20templates%20to%20fit%20the%20requirements%20of%20other%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20an%20expensive%20lift%20from%20a%20practical%20perspective%2C%26quot%3B%20Mignano%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPatibanda-Sanchez%20said%2C%20for%20now%2C%20the%20state%20isn't%20sweating.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20don't%20believe%20that%20Delaware's%20position%20as%20the%20corporate%20leader%20and%20corporate%20capital%20of%20the%20world%20is%20being%20threatened%20in%20any%20significant%20way%2C%26quot%3B%20Patibanda-Sanchez%20said.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%26quot%3BWe%20always%20come%20under%20threat%2C%20though%2C%20because%20states%20are%20always%20trying%20to%20get%20a%20piece%20of%20the%20action.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20February%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdelaware-governor-matt-meyer-corporate-law-elon-musk-bill-ackman-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%