x1152.jpg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG-20241220-WA0016_11zon-1735308654-1200x900.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG-20241220-WA0016_11zon-1735308654-800x600.jpg%20800w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG-20241220-WA0016_11zon-1735308654-600x450.jpg%20600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG-20241220-WA0016_11zon-1735308654-400x300.jpg%20400w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG-20241220-WA0016_11zon-1735308654-200x150.jpg%20200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG-20241220-WA0016_11zon-1735308654-150x113.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-393530%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221482%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ELohith%20dedicated%20around%204%2C000%20square%20metres%20of%20his%20farm%20to%20chrysanthemums.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202018%2C%20Lohith%20took%20his%20first%20major%20step%20into%20commercial%20farming.%20%E2%80%9CI%20built%20my%20farm%20with%20an%20investment%20of%20Rs%2015%20lakh%2C%20which%20included%20building%20a%20polyhouse%20for%20Rs%208%20lakh%2C%20and%20purchasing%2012%2C000%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F277179%2Fengineer-quits-england-job-gerbera-farming-uttar-pradesh-earns-lakhs%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egerbera%20plants%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20a%20nursery%20in%20Pune%20for%20Rs%204%20lakh.%20I%20sold%20about%2040%2C000%20to%2050%2C000%20gerbera%20flowers%20per%20month%20in%20the%20Bengaluru%20market%2C%20making%20around%20Rs%201.5%20lakh%20monthly%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20informs.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20started%20with%20gerbera%20because%20it%20was%20a%20crop%20that%2C%20if%20properly%20maintained%2C%20could%20yield%20for%20more%20th