w.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fvideos%2Fc2djny868x3o%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Rare%20Mushrooms%20Spotted%20for%20the%20First%20Time%20in%20Telangana%2C%20Hinting%20at%20Forest%E2%80%99s%20Secret%20Riches%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EFeature%20image%20courtesy%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newindianexpress.com%2Fgood-news%2F2025%2FAug%2F10%2Frare-blue-pinkgill-shuttlecock-mushrooms-spotted-in-telangana-forests%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20New%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20cool%2C%20damp%20hush%20of%20Telangana%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F473631%2Fmonsoon-travel-hidden-india-offbeat-destinations-hidden-places-to-explore%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emonsoon%20forests%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20colour%20is%20everywhere%20%E2%80%94%20the%20glossy%20green%20of%20fresh%20leaves%2C%20the%20red%20of%20wet%20soil%2C%20the%20yellow%20flicker%20of%20a%20bird%E2%80%99s%20wing.%20But%20this%20season%2C%20something%20else%20has%20caught%20the%20forest%E2%80%99s%20light.%20Something%20unexpected.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20flash%20of%20impossible%20blue%20lay%20nestled%20among%20the%20leaf%20litter%20in%20Komaram%20Bheem%20Asifabad%2C%20catching%20the%20eye%20of%20forest%20staff.%20With%20its%20indigo-blue%20cap%20and%20pale%20gills%20shimmering%20in%20the%20morning%20mist%2C%20the%20blue%20pinkgill%20(%3Cem%3EEntoloma%20hochstetteri%3C%2Fem%3E)%20is%20a%20mushroom%20so%20rare%20in%20India%20that%2C%20until%20recently%2C%20it%20was%20mostly%20known%20from%20faraway%20New%20Zealand%20%E2%80%94%20with%20just%20a%20few%20earlier%20records%20here%2C%20including%20one%20in%20Odisha%20in%201989.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20in%20Kawal%20Tiger%20Reserve%E2%80%99s%20Kaddampeddur%20range%2C%20another%20wonder%20appeared%20%E2%80%94%20the%20shuttlecock%20mushroom%20(%3Cem%3EClathrus%20delicatus%3C%2Fem%3E)%2C%20rising%20like%20a%20tiny%20feathered%20crown%20from%20the%20forest%20floor%2C%20its%20cage-like%20form%20a%20natural%20sculpture.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20are%20not%20common%20roadside%20finds.%20They%20are%20small%20marvels%2C%20spotted%20only%20because%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F463429%2Fandaman-24x7-forest-station-wildlife-crime-deer-wild-pigs%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eforest%20staff%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20researchers%20were%20paying%20close%20attention%2C%20with%20cameras%20and%20notebooks%20ready.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhy%20these%20finds%20matter%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMost%20of%20us%20know%20mushrooms%20as%20the%20quiet%20recyclers%20of%20the%20forest%2C%20turning%20fallen%20wood%20and%20leaves%20into%20rich%20soil.%20They%20rarely%20demand%20notice.%20But%20these%20two%20species%20refuse%20to%20hide.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20blue%20pinkgill%E2%80%99s%20colour%20comes%20from%20azulene%2C%20a%20naturally%20occurring%20blue%20pigment%20also%20found%20in%20some%20flowers%20and%20plants%2C%20but%20rare%20in%20fungi.%20It%E2%80%99s%20what%20gives%20the%20mushroom%20its%20almost%20unreal%20shade%20of%20blue.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20shuttlecock%20mushroom%E2%80%99s%20lattice%20%E2%80%94%20a%20crisscross%2C%20net-like%20structure%20%E2%80%94%20is%20not%20for%20beauty%20alone%3B%20it%20helps%20the%20fungus%20release%20its%20spores%20efficiently%20into%20the%20air.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-08-13T150051.105-1755077457.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20blue%20pinkgill%20mushro